{"tid":1352983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：我希望習總做正確的事","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:00:57.000Z","uid":42431,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5464f4aa649a0dd56c8fb303d6cc70944bae0766","tid":1352983,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"ttps://<a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-07-22/trump-says-china-s-xi-acted-responsibly-in-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-07-22%2Ftrump-says-china-s-xi-acted-responsibly-in-hong-kong-protests&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=013e62be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-07-22/trump-says-china-s-xi-acted-responsibly-in-hong-kong-protests</a><br />\n<br />\nPresident Donald Trump said China&rsquo;s Xi Jinping &ldquo;acted responsibly&rdquo; after seven weekends of demonstrations in Hong Kong and new fears that protesters and the China-backed government are heading toward a violent confrontation.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I think President Xi of China has acted responsibly, very responsibly -- they&rsquo;ve been out there protesting for a long time,&rdquo; Trump told reporters Monday at the White House. <span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;I hope that President Xi will do the right thing,&rdquo; he said, adding that China could stop the protests &ldquo;if they wanted.&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n係咪好positive呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇下隔離個post<br />\n<br />\n特朗普回應：習總負責任地處理香港港示威<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352771</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n改下個title就可以當你狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完美演示如何做帶風向 我警告你班兒登仔以後同我睇撚晒內容先好reply<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji