31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"has acted <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:14.000Z","msg":"When an action began to happen in the past and just finished at the time we are speaking or writing the sentence, we use &quot;Present Perfect Tense&quot;<br />\n<br />\n現在完成式(Present Perfect Tense)的用法﹕<br />\n<br />\n 描述由過去直至現在的事<br />\n           例﹕I have learned English for ten years. (我過去十年一直在學英語。)<br />\n<br />\n過去發生的事<br />\n例﹕I have already done my homework. (我已經做完功課。)<br />\n<br />\n小學畢業先好上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"TEXTBOOK ENGRISH HAHAHAAHAH"},{"pid":"25f94fc029e2d35602776f78ee97b670f6cace65","tid":1352983,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef0d3cc7d659d5043184557a802d93537bdc68c","tid":1352983,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca8558cc618073ead02f67bc170bebbe83d95b3","tid":1352983,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b857efd9046be27f8b1ef6b310b09d9e6faa3d2","tid":1352983,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:25:14.000Z","msg":"When an action began to happen in the past and just finished at the time we are speaking or writing the sentence, we use &quot;Present Perfect Tense&quot;<br />\n<br />\n現在完成式(Present Perfect Tense)的用法﹕<br />\n<br />\n 描述由過去直至現在的事<br />\n           例﹕I have learned English for ten years. (我過去十年一直在學英語。)<br />\n<br />\n過去發生的事<br />\n例﹕I have already done my homework. (我已經做完功課。)<br />\n<br />\n小學畢業先好上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"我做乜要係度教英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好再同我討論英文問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://learnenglish.britishcouncil.org/english-grammar-reference/present-perfect\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flearnenglish.britishcouncil.org%2Fenglish-grammar-reference%2Fpresent-perfect&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=9ef94264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://learnenglish.britishcouncil.org/english-grammar-reference/present-perfect</a><br />\n<br />\nLevel: beginner<br />\n<br />\nThe present perfect is formed from the present tense of the verb have and the past participle of a verb.<br />\n<br />\nWe use the present perfect:<br />\n<br />\nfor something that started in the past and continues in the present:<br />\n<br />\nThey've been married for nearly fifty years.<br />\nShe has lived in Liverpool all her life."},{"pid":"68fefd9cb7996bc28410ff7a87f99045d320b3a1","tid":1352983,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:37:23.000Z","msg":"依家美國係同黑警個種做法一樣有白狗黑狗<br />\n明顯侵侵係到做白狗國會做黑狗"},{"pid":"f866124ab4a80f07fcb112140b0ac003b86598f7","tid":1352983,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"佢咁講好似有d矛盾<br />\nHas acted responsibiy<br />\n如果一直都係responsibly又點會叫習do right thing？"},{"pid":"50b0073c2015dcb2b77397e7a7b8be06f1b94d8c","tid":1352983,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f866124ab4a80f07fcb112140b0ac003b86598f7","tid":1352983,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"佢咁講好似有d矛盾<br />\nHas acted responsibiy<br />\n如果一直都係responsibly又點會叫習do right thing？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:57:24.000Z","msg":"佢話緊has acted repsonsibly 係香港既事，但係一國兩制習總其實唔應該干涉<br />\n<br />\ndo right thing 係講緊貿易協議買農產品果d<br />\n<br />\n我既解讀係唔應該做既野你又係咁做，唔撚該做番d正經野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04ffccda49aa6b8e2330735c198b596cc10ef0e","tid":1352983,"uid":234596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f866124ab4a80f07fcb112140b0ac003b86598f7","tid":1352983,"uid":266924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:38:51.000Z","msg":"佢咁講好似有d矛盾<br />\nHas acted responsibiy<br />\n如果一直都係responsibly又點會叫習do right thing？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"Has acted responsibly 係國家主席身份下佢做嘅嘢係responsible.<br />\n但係Do the right thing係以人嘅身份之下習未有做正確嘅事情。<br />\nActed responsibly 不等於Do the right thing。<br />\n即係好似法官案照法律，判一個小偷死刑。法律條文上面係咁寫法官就係咁判，法官有執行佢嘅職責係responsible, 但係判刑咁重就唔係the right thing。"},{"pid":"653fc4f6dee5c55a21ede27acdbe5d2d6956cdcd","tid":1352983,"uid":86090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb929370052142d05d2a68cc2467cf889be61963","tid":1352983,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}